nk:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ngx1665703195292.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ngx1665703195292.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ngx1665703195292.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ngx1665703195292\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get dynamic information about a server registered with the Uniface Router.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__section_n2x_p5k_gwb\">\n<p class=\"lines\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__lines_ywx_stk_gwb\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">operation GET_SERVER_DYN</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">params</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  numeric</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Srvid</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (I4)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  boolean</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Updatestatic</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: OUT ; (B2)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  entity URSERVERD.UROUTMON : OUT</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">endparams</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__section_nmn_xtk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1195625e85\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__ul_vv4_15k_gwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Srvid</var> (mandatory) is the server’s ID (from the URSERVERS entity) </li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Updatestatic</var>—specifies whether the last returned static servers view\n          should be updated (TRUE) or not (FALSE). </li>\n<li class=\"li\">URSERVERD.UROUTMON—single occurrence of entity URSERVERD.UROUTMON, containing server\n          information. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">URSERVERD.UROUTMON entity</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">Fieldname</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">Packing Code</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">srvid</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Unique server identification, primary key</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">idle</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Ticks since last request</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">idlepercent</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">I1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Percentage idle</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">busy</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Ticks in request</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">busypercent</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">I1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Percentage busy</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">requests</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Number of requests handled</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">srvque</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">I2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Server queue</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ustque</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">I2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">UST queue</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">state</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">C3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">I=idle or B=busy, L=locked or C=has context,\n                S=starting or E=exiting<p class=\"p\">e.g. <code class=\"ph codeph\">ILE</code></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">clthost</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">C256</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Host and IP address of last or current client\n                served</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cltpid</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Process ID of last or current client served</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">transaction</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ngx1665703195292__table_x1n_p5k_gwb__entry__4\">Transaction number when locked</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__section_sbc_n5k_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1195625e371\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If successful, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to the number (zero or 1) of returned\n        USERVERD occurrences. A return of zero must be considered an error and a reason to update\n        the static servers view if the server ID was supplied from it. For more information, see\n          <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"agq1665703194991.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/agq1665703194991.html\" title=\"Get static information about servers registered with the Uniface Router.\">GET_SERVERS</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Otherwise, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html#qln1665702528769__section_fbt_4d2_gwb\">Return Codes</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__section_bbt_s5k_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1195625e397\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__section_tgx_t5k_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1195625e406\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ngx1665703195292__p_d135182e1_d135183e1_d135184e1\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">GET_SERVER_DYN</span> operation gets\n        dynamic information about a server, identified by its server ID, that is registered with the\n        Uniface Router.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530250\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530250\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "GET_SERVER_DYN Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get dynamic information about a server registered with the Uniface Router. operation GET_SERVER_DYN params numeric Srvid : IN ; (I4) boolean Updatestatic : OUT ; (B2) entity URSERVERD.UROUTMON : OUT endparams Parameters Srvid (mandatory) is the server’s ID (from the URSERVERS entity) Updatestatic —specifies whether the last returned static servers view should be updated (TRUE) or not (FALSE). URSERVERD.UROUTMON—single occurrence of entity URSERVERD.UROUTMON, containing server information. Table 1. URSERVERD.UROUTMON entity Fieldname Packing Code Data Type Description srvid I4 Numeric Unique server identification, primary key idle I4 Numeric Ticks since last request idlepercent I1 Numeric Percentage idle busy I4 Numeric Ticks in request busypercent I1 Numeric Percentage busy requests I4 Numeric Number of requests handled srvque I2 Numeric Server queue ustque I2 Numeric UST queue state C3 String I=idle or B=busy, L=locked or C=has context, S=starting or E=exiting e.g. ILE clthost C256 String Host and IP address of last or current client served cltpid I4 Numeric Process ID of last or current client served transaction I4 Numeric Transaction number when locked Return Values If successful, $status is set to the number (zero or 1) of returned USERVERD occurrences. A return of zero must be considered an error and a reason to update the static servers view if the server ID was supplied from it. For more information, see GET_SERVERS . Otherwise, see Return Codes . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The GET_SERVER_DYN operation gets dynamic information about a server, identified by its server ID, that is registered with the Uniface Router. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}